file_content.text: If you're waiting for a pourboire, you're wasting your time. Leave me be.
This is sufficient, I suppose. I'll send word to Malfus that his contribution did not go unnoticed.
I'm not in need of a bodyguard, so kindly give me some space.
I've not had the pleasure to meet a Sith in person. I'm honored by your presence.
Good day, Imperial. All is quiet here for the moment.
